        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-06-13T18:31:54Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Directs the Secretary of Veterans Affairs (VA) to establish a student loan repayment program in which the Secretary repays the undergraduate student loan amounts that veterans owe on any date they incur a service-connected disability that is rated as total.</p> <p>Makes the repayment program applicable only to: (1) veterans who served in the Armed Forces on or after September 11, 2001, and (2) loans made before the veteran entered the Armed Forces.</p>]]></text>
